HAPPY NEW YEAR FROM THE MARINOS!! What a crazy past year and looking forward to things this time around the sun. I hope everyone has a great holiday and stay safe!! Thank you to all my family, friends and clients who have continued to support me. And always a huge thank you to my beautiful wife @misstj for putting up with my shit and being my rock. I hope we all spend the next year focusing on our happiness and mental health. Set your intentions for the new year and stay motivated. Love and take care of those around you but don’t forget to take care of yourself! “The meaning of life is just to be alive.” -Alan Watts
